{"tid":766180,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯嬲撚到喊左出黎","createTime":"2018-08-03T11:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T13:41:47.000Z","uid":21598,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e03b54d98c2ee409141568ddd3ba6addd3b2d356","tid":766180,"uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"第一次望住堆飯會嬲到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .....<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事源係咁,屋企人出去食飯,我唔想岩岩返黎又要再出去,老母話食完之後買返黎比我<br />\r\n問我要咩飯,我話栗米斑腩飯.跟住佢無喇喇話&quot;都係唔好,我每樣夾d比你仲好喇&quot;我心諗,正,唔使食碟頭飯得一個餸,點知原來係惡夢既開始.佢9點幾返到黎我已經餓到不似人形,諗住狗衝打開個飯黎食.開左之後我屌左出聲,當堂怒火中燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  .<br />\r\n<br />\r\n幾條白菜,幾舊豆腐卜,幾條粉絲,n多白飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n十幾年功力既粗口直頭想一次過爆發.......<br />\r\n最後衝左入房偷偷落淚.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到依家成11點我都未食野<br />\r\n仲要比老母屌撚到我仆街...........<br />\r\n<br />\r\n到底有無人會明白,一個餓到仆街,滿心期待既人....面對d咁既餸菜組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n殺撚左我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n利申:好撚委屈.諗起又想喊,邊打邊喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031e2792426d7e50ef04afed0622d2935dc06b04","tid":766180,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"唔好食"},{"pid":"afd2cee8d3c440f17913c0c15ade25386aeedaa4","tid":766180,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"成家係晚上7點42分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f256987f4df8a750e149e26ca0b03e70cc3cf54c","tid":766180,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"睇黎你老母好撚憎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d5de82ac46b10ed58b62dafbdcde3fe8af6805","tid":766180,"uid":188049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e03b54d98c2ee409141568ddd3ba6addd3b2d356","tid":766180,"uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"第一次望住堆飯會嬲到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .....<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事源係咁,屋企人出去食飯,我唔想岩岩返黎又要再出去,老母話食完之後買返黎比我<br />\r\n問我要咩飯,我話栗米斑腩飯.跟住佢無喇喇話&quot;都係唔好,我每樣夾d比你仲好喇&quot;我心諗,正,唔使食碟頭飯得一個餸,點知原來係惡夢既開始.佢9點幾返到黎我已經餓到不似人形,諗住狗衝打開個飯黎食.開左之後我屌左出聲,當堂怒火中燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  .<br />\r\n<br />\r\n幾條白菜,幾舊豆腐卜,幾條粉絲,n多白飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n十幾年功力既粗口直頭想一次過爆發.......<br />\r\n最後衝左入房偷偷落淚.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到依家成11點我都未食野<br />\r\n仲要比